    <section class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Kirim Media / File</h2>

      <p class="mb-2">Endpoint ini memungkinkan Anda mengirim file/media ke nomor WhatsApp.</p>

      <div class="mb-2">
        <span class="font-semibold">Method:</span> <code>POST</code> <br>
        <span class="font-semibold">URL:</span> <code>/wa/send-media</code>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <span class="font-semibold">Form Data:</span>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700">
          <li><code>number</code>: nomor tujuan (contoh: 6281234567890)</li>
          <li><code>caption</code>: opsional, teks pendamping file</li>
          <li><code>file</code>: file yang diupload (jpg, png, mp4, pdf, docx, zip, rar) max 10 MB</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-2">
        <span class="font-semibold">Response sukses:</span>
        <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded overflow-x-auto">
{
  "success": true,
  "number": "6281234567890",
  "caption": "Ini file PDF",
  "media_url": "abc123.pdf"
}
        </pre>
      </div>

      <div>
        <span class="font-semibold">Response gagal:</span>
        <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded overflow-x-auto">
{
  "error": "Ekstensi file tidak diizinkan"
}
        </pre>
      </div>
    </section>